# Access physical display


Scenario: User accesses open physical display remotely
  Given   physical display is unlocked
  When   user access vnc port
  Then   user sees the current active session

Scenario: User accesses locked physical display remotely
  Given   physical display is unlocked
  When   user access vnc port
  Then   user sees the lock screen

Scenario: User accesses logins in to physical display remotely
  Given   physical display is locked
  *       user is connected through vnc
  When   user has entered a valid username and password
  Then   the physical display is logged in
  *      the vnc session is ended
  *      user can reconnect to vnc to see logged in session

Scenario: User accesses locked physical display while in use

Scenario: User accesses locked physical display while in use

